<a href="/questions/1478921-just-finished-jane-steele-loved-the">just finished Jane Steele....loved the book...would appreciate other&#39;s who enjoyed the book suggestions?...I am always looking for good historical fiction...
I&#39;m not great at spelling but thru out the book &#39;Realized&#39; was spelled with an S...anymore there are often so many grammatical issues in books...it&#39;s awful... it takes one out of the story...</a>
