<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">In the UK, &quot;realized&quot; IS spelled &quot;realised.&quot; I do see a lot of typos in some books, but I wouldn&apos;t have batted an eye at that one.<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">In the UK, "realized" IS spelled "realised." I do see a lot of typos in some books, but I wouldn't have batted an eye at that one.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
