        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3920053432" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer9069812072796055830">2.5 stars. This book should have been much better than it was. It was well researched and about a fascinating period of New York’s history- so what went wrong? The pacing was off. Very off. This book literally sent me off to sleep on several occasions where a few pages earlier I was really engaged. The themes of establishing a police force, political corruption, child prostitution, racism against the Irish, extreme poverty, the 5 points were terribly interesting but somehow got lost.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


